>\ns.get(url, params=params)<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n自己搵個python excel lib研究吓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T14:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7f150c5cde3de746036bb059bfd35e3a0522ab","tid":914711,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T00:44:38.000Z","msg":"如果用shell script做，斷估求其用for、while loop做得<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<br />\n#! /bin/bash<br />\n<br />\nOIFS=$IFS<br />\nIFS='<br />\n'<br />\n<br />\nwhile read -r line ; do<br />\n     download_file=$(echo ''$line'' | cut -d'' '' -f2) <br />\n     #或者 echo ''$line'' | awk '{print $2}' <br />\n     wget --save-cookies cookies.txt \\<br />\n               --keep-session-cookies \\<br />\n               --post-data &rsquo;user=foo&amp;password=bar&lsquo; \\<br />\n                --delete-after \\<br />\n                <a href=\"http://server.com/auth.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fserver.com%2Fauth.php&d=w9DZdEvovJxVlOaX2L8sP8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2e9dd3cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://server.com/auth.php</a>  -q ''$download_file''  <br />\n   done &lt; your_excel_txt_file<br />\n<br />\nunset IFS<br />\nIFS=$OIFS<br />\n<br />\nexit 0<br />\n<br />\n一行一行讀取直到file讀完，script完全冇測試，憑空斷估寫，只用作參考，唔一定work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}